cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CC, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and recognizing textual entailment. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new method to investigate the quality of training data for the RTE task. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with machine learning and natural language processing. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the impact of hidden bias on the performance of neural network models. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with the quality of a large corpus designed for the RTE task.
